Rating: 4
This is so ridiculously good that I have made 5 batches in the past 10 days. The trickiest part for me is adding the cream to the caramel without it all seizing up; reheating the cream-caramel mixture to melt the lumps tends to overly darken the caramel and create bitter/burnt off notes. I found that heating up the cream and adding it very slowly to the caramel while stirring vigorously to be helpful

