Rating: 4
So delicious!!!!! I had the same trouble with the conversion process as an earlier reviewer and suspected my bowl (kitchenaid ice cream attachment) wasn't sufficiently cold. After 1 hour - nothing, the mix was still liquid. So, I poured the liquid back into a bowl, stuck it in the fridge, put my ice cream bowl into the freezer and set it to its coldest setting. Left it overnight. About 14 hours later, the liquid was fine, the bowl was absolutely frozen, and I had ice cream in 15 minutes. Two lessons - make sure your equipment is adequately cold and the ice cream mix can withstand the abuse of trying more than once.

